    "id": "ecology",
    "name": "Ecology",
    "description": "Ecological systems and their collapse patterns.",
    "invariants": [
      "Ecosystem boundaries, including biotic and abiotic components, MUST be explicitly defined.",
      "Ecological interactions and relationships (e.g., predator-prey, symbiosis) MUST be explicitly modeled and traceable.",
