      "The scope of ecological models and simulations MUST be clearly defined, with assumptions and limitations stated.",
      "Mechanisms for system stability, resilience, and feedback loops MUST be identified and understood.",
      "Human impacts on the ecosystem and their consequences MUST be explicitly considered."
